Package edu.ncsu.csc216.pack_scheduler.course.roll

Class CourseRoll

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.ncsu.csc216.pack_scheduler.course.roll.CourseRoll

  • public class CourseRoll
extends java.lang.Object
    CourseRoll sets the enrollment cap of the courses between the set bounds. It also adds and removes students from the wait list.
    Author:
    TJ
